    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/e83026905e5ab7edefb7d5469d913242.poster.avif?t=1769689139\" width=1170 height=657 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/e83026905e5ab7edefb7d5469d913242.webm?t=1769689139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座研究院一度是科研的巅峰——直到一场灾难性事件让它迷失在虚空中，被衰变所侵蚀，连同其深藏的秘密一同迈向沉寂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从冷冻休眠中苏醒，肩负着修复研究院、查明灾难始末的使命。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《The Lift》是一款沉浸式第一人称模拟游戏，将令人满足的设施翻新与一场由故事驱动的神秘冒险之旅融为一体。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/7fea02de6e2e16ee0733be6873caf973.poster.avif?t=1769689139\" width=1170 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/7fea02de6e2e16ee0733be6873caf973.webm?t=1769689139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/9f8cbb28be78bfbabc19d505b916d663.poster.avif?t=1769689139\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/9f8cbb28be78bfbabc19d505b916d663.webm?t=1769689139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一层都是一个有着独特挑战的大型翻新项目。你可以自由安排游戏节奏，上至复杂的电力工程，下至基础的家具修理，一切由你自己掌控。活用各种小工具，制造你所需要的物品，让研究院重现昔日辉煌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/0daad4e8fe83d0c568df0804a5f2eca7.poster.avif?t=1769689139\" width=1170 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/0daad4e8fe83d0c568df0804a5f2eca7.webm?t=1769689139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/decfadf73c0a5fee9384d69dbbd80f09.poster.avif?t=1769689139\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/decfadf73c0a5fee9384d69dbbd80f09.webm?t=1769689139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让升降梯变成你的移动基地，穿梭于研究院各处。探索多样的生态环境，开启隐藏的秘密区域，结识个性鲜明的角色，完成他们的委托。逐步拼凑出那场惊天事变背后，那令人匪夷所思的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/be78566c69139ae1cd461c8d5d877187.poster.avif?t=1769689139\" width=1170 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/be78566c69139ae1cd461c8d5d877187.webm?t=1769689139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/43ad9da585c42046d1c759638edb90cb.poster.avif?t=1769689139\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283240/extras/43ad9da585c42046d1c759638edb90cb.webm?t=1769689139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让数十种精密设备重获新生——小到售货机和发电机，大到卫星天线、有自我意识的电脑甚至是反应堆。使用多种零件搭建电路，诊断故障，铺设线路，调控供电与扭矩，让每一个系统都起死回生。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 令人满足的修理工模拟 + 沉浸式叙事驱动冒险</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 可供探索和翻修的大型研究设施</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 复杂的电气工程项目</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 古怪但实用的小工具（例如：异常清洁光束、胶枪等）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 以循环利用为核心的制造系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 受苏联复古未来主义启发的高互动性世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 个性鲜明、全程配音的角色，以及引人入胜的任务和故事</p>",
